    "Name": "Warlord",
    "Details": "The WLD-1P is armed only with two Large and three Medium Pulse Lasers, but is very mobile thanks to its large 300 XL engine, MASC and five jump jets. This allows the 'Mech to maneuver around and flank foes, hitting them with the pulse lasers at weaker locations that are easily penetrated. The 'Mech is cooled by twelve double heat sinks, meaning some care in regards to heat build up has to be taken.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Easy to Maintain</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.08</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Lower, Right Lower</color>",
